      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" lang=\"en\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"generator\" content=\"pandoc\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes\" />\n  <title>Release Notes for MX25LM51245G OCTOSPI Component Driver</title>\n  <style type=\"text/css\">\n      code{white-space: pre-wrap;}\n      span.smallcaps{font-variant: small-caps;}\n      span.underline{text-decoration: underline;}\n      div.column{display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 50%;}\n  </style>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"_htmresc/mini-st_2020.css\" />\n  <!--[if lt IE 9]>\n    <script src=\"//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/html5shiv/3.7.3/html5shiv-printshiv.min.js\"></script>\n  <![endif]-->\n  <link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/x-icon\" href=\"_htmresc/favicon.png\" />\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-lg-4\">\n<center>\n<h1 id=\"release-notes-for\">Release Notes for</h1>\n<h1 id=\"mx25lm51245g-component-driver\"><mark>MX25LM51245G Component Driver </mark></h1>\n<p>Copyright \u00a9 2017-2023 STMicroelectronics<br />\n</p>\n<a href=\"https://www.st.com\" class=\"logo\"><img src=\"_htmresc/st_logo_2020.png\" alt=\"ST logo\" /></a>\n</center>\n<h1 id=\"purpose\">Purpose</h1>\n<p>This driver provides a set of functions offered by MX25LM51245G OCTOSPI component</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-lg-8\">\n<h1 id=\"update-history\">Update History</h1>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"collapse-section14\" checked aria-hidden=\"true\"> <label for=\"collapse-section14\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><strong>V3.0.3 / 21-Feb-2025</strong></label>\n<div>\n<h2 id=\"main-changes\">Main Changes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Update SIOO field as optional</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"collapse-section13\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <label for=\"collapse-section13\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><strong>V3.0.2 / 29-June-2023</strong></label>\n<div>\n<h2 id=\"main-changes\">Main Changes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Update license</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"collapse-section12\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <label for=\"collapse-section12\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><strong>V3.0.1 / 18-October-2022</strong></label>\n<div>\n<h2 id=\"main-changes-1\">Main Changes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix spelling errors</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"collapse-section11\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <label for=\"collapse-section11\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><strong>V3.0.0 / 21-June-2022</strong></label>\n<div>\n<h2 id=\"main-changes-2\">Main Changes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Drivers updated to rely on HAL XSPI instead of HAL OSPI</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"dependencies\">Dependencies</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>This version is to be used with HAL library containing the XSPI drivers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"backward-compatibility\">Backward Compatibility</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>This version breaks the compatibility with previous versions</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"collapse-section10\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <label for=\"collapse-section10\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><strong>V2.0.8 / 01-February-2022</strong></label>\n<div>\n<h2 id=\"main-changes-3\">Main Changes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Update license</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"collapse-section9\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <label for=\"collapse-section9\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><strong>V2.0.7 / 24-December-2021</strong></label>\n<div>\n<h2 id=\"main-changes-4\">Main Changes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Align command structure with HAL</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"collapse-section8\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <label for=\"collapse-section8\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><strong>V2.0.6 / 04-May-2021</strong></label>\n<div>\n<h2 id=\"main-changes-5\">Main Changes</h2>",
