      "content": "<ul>\n<li>Fix spelling warnings</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"collapse-section7\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <label for=\"collapse-section7\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><strong>V2.0.5 / 31-December-2020</strong></label>\n<div>\n<h2 id=\"main-changes-6\">Main Changes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Check Misra-C 2012 coding rules compliance</li>\n<li>Formatting update</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"collapse-section6\"  aria-hidden=\"true\"> <label for=\"collapse-section6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><strong>V2.0.4 / 24-Juin-2020</strong></label>\n<div>\n<h2 id=\"main-changes-7\">Main Changes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Codespell miss-spelling errors correction.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"collapse-section5\"  aria-hidden=\"true\"> <label for=\"collapse-section5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><strong>V2.0.3 / 27-March-2020</strong></label>\n<div>\n<h2 id=\"main-changes-8\">Main Changes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Update mx25lm51245g.c so that, based on MSEL bit definition in OCTOSPI_CR register, resort to <em>s_command.FlashSelect</em> instead of <em>s_command.FlashId</em>.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"collapse-section4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <label for=\"collapse-section4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><strong>V2.0.2 / 05-February-2020</strong></label>\n<div>\n<h2 id=\"main-changes-9\">Main Changes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Minor change to fix misra warnings</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"collapse-section3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <label for=\"collapse-section3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><strong>V2.0.1 / 15-November-2019</strong></label>\n<div>\n<h2 id=\"main-changes-10\">Main Changes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Minor change on mx25lm51245g.h driver</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"collapse-section2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <label for=\"collapse-section2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><strong>V2.0.0 / 30-October-2019</strong></label>\n<div>\n<h2 id=\"main-changes-11\">Main Changes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>First Official Release of MX25LM51245G octal SPI Component drivers in line with STM32Cube BSP drivers development guidelines (UM2298)</li>\n<li>The component drivers are composed of\n<ul>\n<li>component core drivers files: mx25lm51245g.h/.c</li>\n<li>component configuration file mx25lm51245g_conf_template.h file</li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"backward-compatibility-1\">Backward Compatibility</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>This version breaks the compatibility with previous versions</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"collapse-section1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <label for=\"collapse-section1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><strong>V1.0.0 / 07-August-2017</strong></label>\n<div>\n<h2 id=\"main-changes-12\">Main Changes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>First official release of <strong>MX25LM51245G</strong> octal SPI driver</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"sticky\">\nFor complete documentation on <mark>STM32 Microcontrollers</mark> , visit: <span style=\"font-color: blue;\"><a href=\"http://www.st.com/STM32\">www.st.com</a></span>\n</footer>\n</body>\n</html>",
